==Martuthunira==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ŋanaɳa/}}
===Etymology===
From Proto-Ngayarda ''*nganarna'', from Proto-Pama-Nyungan ''*ngana''.
===Pronoun===
'''nganarna'''

